Description.SourceString:
Thank you for being with us for this incredible journey!

Earn a 5th Anniversary Crown for each original character, unlock event items in the Bloodweb, log in for additional Iridescent Shards, and explore new perks daily in the Shrine of Secrets.

During the Anniversary Event when the community earns enough Crowns, everyone unlocks exclusive outfits for David King and the Wraith and two universal charms!

Visit our social channels for more information on the event and the unlockable rewards!

The Midnight Grove event is here!

Now pumpkins are growing in the Realm of the Entity and can be destroyed to gain bonus Bloodpoints and the chance to find a trick or a treat. Additionally, previous Halloween items are returning to the Bloodweb.

An Event Tome has been added for the Archives, only playable during the Midnight Grove event! Play the new Event Tome to unlock exclusive event cosmetics for our newest Survivor, Mikaela Reid, and for The Doctor, as well as three new charms!

Visit our social channels for more information on the Midnight Grove event and the unlockable rewards!
